      <title>拖拉機供應公司因成本緩解而超出第一季利潤預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tractor-supply-beats-first-quarter-profit-estimates-easing-costs-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，Tractor Supply 的第一季度利潤超出了華爾街的預期，運輸成本的緩解以及對農業用品零售商寵物食品和園藝產品的穩定需求提振了其利潤率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/tractor-supply-beats-first-quarter-profit-estimates-easing-costs-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
